rn CSButtonReturn()" onmouseout="return CSIShow(/*CMP*/''button5'',0)" onmouseover="return CSIShow(/*CMP*/''button5'',1)" target="_top"><img border="0" height="24" name="button5" src="http://steamsupport.valvesoftware.com:80/Home/Update%20images/Tabs-FAQ_out.gif" width="64"/></a></csobj></td> <td align="left" colspan="3" height="24" valign="top" width="139" xpos="541"><img border="0" height="24" src="http://steamsupport.valvesoftware.com:80/Home/Update%20images/Tabs-FAQ_Border.gif" width="135"/></td> <td height="24" width="1"><spacer height="24" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr height="90"> <td colspan="2" height="1097" rowspan="2" width="19"><spacer height="1097" type="block" width="19"/></td> <td align="left" colspan="12" height="90" valign="top" width="632" xpos="19"> <table bgcolor="#6a6f82" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" cool="" gridx="16" gridy="16" height="90" showgridx="" showgridy="" width="632"> <tr height="24"> <td height="89" rowspan="2" width="204"><spacer height="89" type="block" width="204"/></td> <td height="24" width="427"><spacer height="24" type="block" width="427"/></td> <td height="24" width="1"><spacer height="24" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr height="65"> <td align="left" height="65" valign="top" width="427" xpos="204"><img border="0" height="40" src="http://steamsupport.valvesoftware.com:80/Home/Update%20images/PageTitles-News.gif" width="223"/></td> <td height="65" width="1"><spacer height="65" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr cntrlrow="" height="1"> <td height="1" width="204"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="204"/></td> <td height="1" width="427"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="427"/></td> <td height="1" width="1"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> </table> </td> <td height="1097" rowspan="2" width="29"><spacer height="1097" type="block" width="29"/></td> <td height="90" width="1"><spacer height="90" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr height="1007"> <td align="left" colspan="2" height="1007" valign="top" width="68" xpos="19"> <table bgcolor="#6a6f82" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" cool="" gridx="16" gridy="16" height="1007" showgridx="" showgridy="" width="68"> <tr height="1006"> <td height="1006" width="67"><spacer height="1006" type="block" width="67"/></td> <td height="1006" width="1"><spacer height="1006" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr cntrlrow="" height="1"> <td height="1" width="67"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="67"/></td> <td height="1" width="1"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> </table> </td> <td align="left" bgcolor="#6a6f82" colspan="9" content="" csgroup="01175B50" csheight="1007" height="1007" valign="top" width="496" xpos="87"> <ul> <li type="square"><font color="white" face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>*** SERVER ARE ONLINE! ***</b><br/> </font><font size="3"><br/> </font> <li type="square"><font color="white" face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>*DoD beta 2.0 is available</b><b>*</b><b><br/> </b></font><font size="3"><br/> </font> <li type="square"><font color="white" face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>Become A Beta Tester!</b></font><font size="3"><br/> 											 											 											If you''re interested in becoming a Beta Tester, fill out our <a href="http://beta.valvesoftware.com" target="_new">Survey</a><br/> </font><font size="2"></font><font size="3"><br/> </font> <li type="square"><font color="white" face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>From the Dev Team:<br/> </b></font><font face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>Planned Changes/Additions:</b><b><br/> </b></font><font face="Times New Roman,Georgia,Times" size="3">--------------------------<br/> 											- Hostage AI upgrade<br/> 											- New Counter-Strike hostage rescue map<br/> 											- Vote/Kick<br/> 											- General code optimization pass (client and server)<br/> 											- Anti-Cheating system incorporated<br/> 											- Allow server administrators to bind server to specific IP<br/> 											- Allow server administrators to bind server to specific port<br/> 											- Allow command line switches for server administrators<br/> 											- Rework Para accuracy<br/> 											- Make left and right handed models switchable on the fly<br/> 											- Incorporate Tracker into Steam beta<br/> 											- Remove "Use Shooting" from Counter-Strike<br/> 											- Remove speed penalty when falling off an object.Will only apply when jumping.<br/> 											- Allow muting of other player''s text messages.<br/> <br/> </font><font face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>Planned Bug fixes:</b><b><br/> </b></font><font face="Times New Roman,Georgia,Times" size="3">--------------------------<br/> 											- Default voice to use DirectSound by default<br/> 											- Allow Steam to autoupdate itself<br/> 											- Fix demo playback.<br/> 											- Fix bug that allows a player automatically chosen as the VIP to keep their weapon.<br/> 											- Fix exploit that allows Counter-Terrorists to look like Terrorists in certain maps.<br/> 											- Fix missing entries in the spectator menu.<br/> <br/> </font><font face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>Recent Changes/Additions:</b><b><br/> </b></font><font face="Times New Roman,Georgia,Times" size="3">--------------------------<br/> 											- HLTV UI upgrade<br/> 											- Returned crosshairs for C4 and the knife<br/> 											- Added de_chateau to mapcycle<br/> <br/> </font><font face="Arial,Helvetica,Geneva,Swiss,SunSans-Regular" size="3"><b>Recent Bugfixes:</b><b><br/> </b></font><font face="Times New Roman,Georgia,Times" size="3">--------------------------<br/> 											- Fixed jittery jump bug<br/> 											- Fixed server list filtering bug in which the game filter attribute was lost<br/> 											- Fixed string 595 error when clicking server list filter button<br/> 											- Fixed problem with Terrorist and Counter-Terrorist menus not looking correct after changing teams<br/> </font> <p></p> </li></li></li></li></ul> </td> <td align="left" bgcolor="#6a6f82" content="" csgroup="01175B50" csheight="1007" height="1007" valign="top" width="68" xpos="583"></td> <td height="1007" width="1"><spacer height="1007" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr height="46"> <td height="46" width="2"><spacer height="46" type="block" width="2"/></td> <td align="left" colspan="14" height="46" valign="top" width="678" xpos="2"><img border="0" height="43" src="http://steamsupport.valvesoftware.com:80/Home/Update%20images/Page-Bottom.gif" width="675"/></td> <td height="46" width="1"><spacer height="46" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr height="29"> <td colspan="9" height="29" width="302"><spacer height="29" type="block" width="302"/></td> <td align="left" colspan="2" height="29" valign="top" width="175" xpos="302"><img border="0" height="29" src="http://steamsupport.valvesoftware.com:80/Home/Update%20images/Bottom-VALVE1.gif" width="81"/></td> <td colspan="4" height="29" width="203"><spacer height="29" type="block" width="203"/></td> <td height="29" width="1"><spacer height="29" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr height="26"> <td colspan="6" height="26" width="133"><spacer height="26" type="block" width="133"/></td> <td align="left" colspan="7" height="26" valign="top" width="450" xpos="133"><img border="0" height="19" src="http://steamsupport.valvesoftware.com:80/Home/Update%20images/Bottom-Links.gif" usemap="#Bottom-Linksad2d481" width="412"/></td> <td colspan="2" height="26" width="97"><spacer height="26" type="block" width="97"/></td> <td height="26" width="1"><spacer height="26" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr height="28"> <td align="left" colspan="15" height="28" valign="top" width="680" xpos="0"><img border="0" height="28" src="http://steamsupport.valvesoftware.com:80/Home/Update%20images/Bottom-COPY1.gif" width="678"/></td> <td height="28" width="1"><spacer height="28" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> <tr cntrlrow="" height="1"> <td height="1" width="2"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="2"/></td> <td height="1" width="17"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="17"/></td> <td height="1" width="9"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="9"/></td> <td height="1" width="59"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="59"/></td> <td height="1" width="3"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="3"/></td> <td height="1" width="43"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="43"/></td> <td height="1" width="17"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="17"/></td> <td height="1" width="129"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="129"/></td> <td height="1" width="23"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="23"/></td> <td height="1" width="53"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="53"/></td> <td height="1" width="122"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="122"/></td> <td height="1" width="64"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="64"/></td> <td height="1" width="42"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="42"/></td> <td height="1" width="68"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="68"/></td> <td height="1" width="29"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="29"/></td> <td height="1" width="1"><spacer height="1" type="block" width="1"/></td> </tr> </table> <map name="Textimage-News4dbfb53"><area coords="19,2,182,19" href="#" shape="rect" target="_top"/></map><map name="bottom-logo496a198"></map></td> </tr> </table> <map name="Bottom-Linksad2d481"><area coords="353,4,406,15" href="mailto:steamsupport@valvesoftware.com" shape="rect" target="_top"/><area coords="316,4,341,15" href="../Faq/FAQ.htm" shape="rect" target="_top"/><area coords="234,4,307,15" href="http://www.chatbear.com/cgi-bin/board.pl?boardid=1041&amp;view=flatold" shape="rect" target="_top"/><area coords="183,4,218,15" href="../BetaSupport/support.htm" sha