hile you''re in-game.<br> <br> <!-- At its core, Steam is a distributed file system and shared set of technology components that can be implemented into any software application.<br> <br> With Steam, developers are given integrated tools for direct-content publishing, flexible billing, ensured-version control, anti-cheating, anti-piracy, and more.<br> <br> --> Check out the full <a href="/index.php?area=features">feature list</a>, and <a href="/index.php?area=getsteamnow">install Steam</a> today!<br> </div>   ',NOW(),NOW());
